                        <h1>GUIDE FOR SOPOT’S BUDGET</h1>
                    </header>
                    <p>For the request of <strong>City Council in Sopot</strong> I created an unique budget bulletin based on infographics. It is citizens-friendly thanks to the Sopoccy family, who guide the reader through. It’s a multigenerational family, and they describe city budget through their interests and their actual life stage and position. Each of them has one card, where city expenses which he or she benefits from are described.</p>
                    <h3>Attractiveness</h3>
                    <p>BBudget is a complicated document and it took me many hours to untangle the financial puzzles. I’m proud of final effect, which is 8 slides dedicated to city expenses illustrated by means of icons and graphics. Even seemingly boring subject as budget can be attractively presented. Of course thanks to visualization! </p>
                    <h3>Usage</h3>
                    <p>Such brochure can be used in many ways. I recommend it especially for online usage, because it has great viral potential in social media. It also can be send by e – mail or be downloaded for a website. If printed, it can take interesting form of postcards, posters, folder or installation and other</p>
