                        <h1>Start Up Contest</h1>
                    </header>
                    <p><strong>Start Up Contest</strong> is an event which connect investors with start-up companies and also enable direct intearction beettwen them. To meet the organizators’ needs, I designed infographics which descirbe stages of the contest. I displayed in easy and readableway, how step by step young company can (in final effect) win 200 thousand Euro for its buisiness concept.</p>
                    <h3>Message fit for the target group</h3>
                    <p>Using icons, arrows and boxes I presented the whole process of participaitionand crucial deadline’s. Message was aimed at target audience – active and young people who are keen on new technologies. Infographic sholud save their time by not reading long, boring e – mails and simplify the registartion procedure. I think it worked, because many people were interested in entering the conest! ;) </p>
