                        <h1>Interactive brand - launch</h1>
                    </header>
                    <p>Dla <strong>Insoft Consulting</strong> supports buissnes processes for others companies. To show how the company had recently changed, I design the animation, which shows it in an interactive way in only several dozen seconds.The animation accompanied the launch of the brand. It was the main channel of communicating the modifications in the brand image. Its premiere took place during a confreance organised for their ten years annivesary. The animation enhances the way of informing customers and stakeholders about Insoft’s Consulting rebranding. It shortly tells the story about ideas and values that stand by this brand and shows lifting of the old logo. It also presents a new visual identity. I strongly recommend this way of changes and improvement presenation and for every company that wants to stands. Customer attention guranteed! ;) </p>
