                        <h1>Mutual development directions</h1>
                    </header>
                    <p>Be means of infographic I invited many people from Gdańsk and neighboring areas for Gdańsk Metropolitan Area'sconference. The purpose of meeting was to discuss further mutual directions for development the Area and actions, which leads to economic consolidation of Pomeranian Region.</p>
                    <h3>Invitation that stands out</h3>
                    <p>I created icons, graphics and colors, which are in line with visual identity of GMA. I held to its main concept, which is represented in their logo. This is an aspiration to community and synergy among every self governments associated in GMA, and keeping their individual spirit at the same time.</p>
                    <h3>summary</h3>
                    <footer>
